Improvements from 1.6 to 1.7
----------------------------

  1. Resurrect and RessurrectID -> MassResurrect

  2. Cloaked creatures now block enemy's LOS but not friendly's LOS.

  3. Fixed life 0. Creatures didn't die when they reached 0 life. Now
     they do.

  4. Fixed Load last name from savefile.

  5. Added lots of new stats in and set them appropriately for each
     creature.

  6. Movement points as float rather than integer.

  7. Modified end-of-turn healing to heal all appropriate stats.

  8. Modified existing combat routine to take into account negative
     combat. We can now make creatures whose attacks heal instead of
     hurt.

  9. Modified existing combat routine to take into account affecting
     different/multiple stats other than life. Now we can make
     creatures that attack any stat or combination of stats. Such as
     intelligence or magic resistance etc.

 10. Added 1 new paragraph to the docs.

 11. Roper, Wasp Nest, Pool, Volcano, Apple Tree are now ordinary items
     which have SpecialCombat.

 12. Modified RangedCombat routine to take into account CR_LOS. Now we
     can make creatures which have distance weapons that don't require
     line of sight.

 13. Added new predicates: AttacksLiving, AttacksUndead, isUndead

 14. Modified maiming routine to not maim on negative combat.

 15. We can now have creatures that gain or lose flying ability.

 16. Lich and Lich Lord and Raise Dead have been modified appropriately.

 17. There was a bug with Magic Sword and Magic Knife: If the wizard
     already had MAX_COMBAT and then cast Magic Sword or Magic Knife
     then he did NOT gain the abiltiy to attack undeads because the
     sword/knife did not get applied.  This is now fixed. The routine
     is now much shorter also.

 18. We can now make creatures which cannot attack living creatures,
     only undeads.

 19. We can now make creatures whose specialcombat affects very
     specific groups of creatures and any combination of stats.

 20. Info Screen graphing is now even better!

 21. ShadowForm, .Shadow, ShadowFormID -> Irvine's_Invulnerability

 22. Heal and HealID -> Restoration.

 23. Info screen has now been revamped to show all the new stats in a
     graphical manner.



@EndNode

