Improvements from 1.7.3 to 1.7.4
--------------------------------

  1. "fixed" LichLord, Simulacrum, Replicate, Vortex.

  2. Show allies on number keys. + change the docs.

  3. Allegedly fixed it so a wizard in a castle or tree can attack
     enemies.

  4. Joe made me put in numeric keypad support.

  5. put in new stat in cast.tex called CAST_GROWTH because the
     computer just cast 6 raise deads on 6 different orange jellies.

  6. Things like walls and pits can now be cast ON growths.


