Improvements from 1.7.4 to 1.7.5
--------------------------------

  1. Fixed that annoying empty dead cell bug.

  2. Fixed Tempests so they don't distort space.

  3. Sometimes the Bonus Spell window ONLY displays Hide spells. Once
     this starts it never seems to stop; every bonus spell for the rest
     of the game is displayed as a Hide spell.

  4. New method of showing what stats are attacked by combat.

  5. Optimize the highlight routine.

  6. Purple combat conflicted with pink recovery so I changed Combat to
     BROWN.

  7. Growth rates were incredibly high so I doubled GCEILING to slow
     them down some.

  8. Fixed the DarkWood so they now attack and while I was at it I
     changed their abilities and description a bit.

  9. RMB now cancels info screens properly.

 10. Shortened ScreenShakes.

 11. Fixed Touch of God to set CombatApply Combat and Ranged Combat for
     Life.

 12. Now Info screen shows BrainBoost, MagicShield and Armour powerups.

 13. Team Icon now displayed on Score Screen and TeamScore screen.

 14. Collapsing meditations now give at least 2 spells to pick from.

 15. Team scores are now displayed but they are not sorted correctly.

 16. Pick your bonus spell even if it is only 1. This way you @{i}know@{ui} that
     you got a bonus spell and you know exactly what you got as a bonus
     spell.

 17. The old sound system hogs 2 audio channels. As a quick fix I just
     commented out the code for 1 of the channels so now it only
     uses/hogs 1 channel.


@EndNode

